{"tid":760892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"#MeToo成內地禁詞 網民改為「俺也一樣」仍遭封殺","createTime":"2018-07-30T02:54:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T04:16:02.000Z","uid":147522,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"143a57185ecdfa2b77004e8e1eba9a413c9247ad","tid":760892,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T02:54:29.000Z","msg":"反性侵和反性騷的「#MeToo」運動，據稱成為內地微博禁詞後，網民想出用中文「俺也一樣」來代替。沒想到「俺也一樣」目前也用不了，內地網民說這種現象真是荒誕又可悲。<br />\n<br />\n內地公益界和知識圈，最近接連有女性出面揭露曾遭性騷擾或性侵，涉事者不乏形象良好的公眾人物。一時之間，中國版的「#MeToo」運動不斷擴散。<br />\n<br />\n有內地傳陸發出問卷後，不到24小時就收到超過1700例和性騷擾、性侵有關的故事，而這些受害者絕大多數選擇了沉默。<br />\n<br />\n然而，在國外媒體也紛紛報道中國內地的「#MeToo」風潮後，「#MeToo」卻開始在內地社群媒體成為禁詞。從北京新浪微博可見，網民因此改用中文的「俺也一樣」來代替，並指這樣的表達真是「既搞笑又悲壯」。<br />\n<br />\n結果，沒想到連「俺也一樣」隨後也步入「#MeToo」後塵而用不了。網民嘆問「荒誕不荒誕、可悲不可悲」。有人則將「俺也一樣」延伸為「俺也一樣涼了」、「老子也是」。"},{"pid":"88ce16cf050881c505dc20e944d83b946970359b","tid":760892,"uid":131691,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T02:56:52.000Z","msg":"但... 但係中國共產黨唔係尊重女權主義嘅咩？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/30/105649_9bf2e7ad93a20ebc871655263f32fc29.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F105649_9bf2e7ad93a20ebc871655263f32fc29.jpeg&h=a1fb5a47&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"121eccfe60944db666487a002f320769754d6002","ti